<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>API Documentation</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1 class="mb-4">Attendance API Documentation</h1>

        <div class="card mb-4">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h2>Authentication</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p>To access the API, you must include the following API key as a query parameter in the request:</p>
                <pre><code>?api_key=<%= apiKey %></code></pre>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card mb-4">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h2>Endpoint: Fetch Attendance Data</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3>GET <code><%= apiUrl %></code></h3>
                <p>This endpoint allows you to fetch attendance data from one or multiple branches.</p>

                <h4>Query Parameters:</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><code>branch</code> (optional): The name of the branch to fetch data from. If omitted, data from all branches will be fetched.</li>
                    <li><code>api_key</code> (required): The API key for authentication.</li>
                </ul>

                <h4>Example Request:</h4>
                <pre><code>curl -X GET "<%= apiUrl %>?branch=Main%20Branch&api_key=<%= apiKey %>"</code></pre>

                <h4>Response:</h4>
                <p>The API returns a JSON object with the attendance data. Example:</p>
                <pre><code>{
    "success": true,
    "data": [
        {
            "uid": "123",
            "timestamp": "2024-08-14T08:45:00",
            "status": "1",
            "punch": "0",
            "branch": "Main Branch"
        }
    ]
}</code></pre>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.6/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
